               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms1_i1">
                     <locus from="3r" to="29v">Fols 3r–29v</locus>
                     <title>Asmāt prayers for the week</title>
                     <note>Introduction, fol. 3r-5v; Monday, fol. 5v-8r; Tuesday, fol. 8r-14r; Wednesday, fol. 14r-18r; Thursday, fol. 18v-20r; Friday, fol. 20r-24r; Saturday, fol. 24r-27r; Sunday, fol. 27r-29v
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms1_i2">
                     <locus from="29v" to="40v">Fols 29v–40v</locus>
                     <title>Prayer to Jesus, For the sake of the saints
                     </title>                     
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms1_i3">
                     <locus from="40v" to="56v">Fols 40v–56v</locus>
                     <title>Anaphora of Mary by Cyriacus of Behnesa
                     </title>                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘነበበ፡ በመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ሕርያቆስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘብሔረ፡ ብኅንሳ፡
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms1_i4">
                     <locus from="56v" to="57r">Fols 56v–57r</locus>
                     <title>Booklet of Prayer. Selection
                     </title>                  
                     <note>Introduction on the origin of the Booklet of Prayer</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ከመዝ፡ ምጽአታ፡ ወነበረ፡ ፩መኰንን፡ በሀገረ፡ አፍንጊ፡ ወሶበ፡ ቦአ፡ ውስተ፡ ጸማዕት፡ ከመ፡ ያሥምሮ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
