                  <additions><list><item xml:id="a1">Texts in a secondary hand: Commemoration days of the apostles, fol. 1r; Excerpt of Ṣoma deggwā, fol. 1v-2r; Life of Abba Samuel and his monastery, fol. 1v-2ብ, 58v; Monasteries of Ethiopia and a dispute between Orthodox and Catholics from the Raʼeya Sinodā, fol. 57v-58r
                     
                  </item><item xml:id="e1">Seal of the Institute of Ethiopian Studies, ff. 1a and 58b.</item><item xml:id="e2">Copied for ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ, fol. 3r and throughout; Note of ownership by አባ፡ ተክለ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አባይ, fol. 3r; </item></list></additions>
